    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Tā diezgan bieža parādība, jo nosaukumi vēsturiski, bet pēc tam pilsētas/ciemi dabū robežas \"sadalot\" nosaukumu. Rīgā piemēram arī Dreiliņi <a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=13/56.94240/24.23524\">https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=13/56.94240/24.23524</a> Berģi <a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=14/56.98753/24.30335\">https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=14/56.98753/24.30335</a> Suži <a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=14/57.01875/24.20953\">https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=14/57.01875/24.20953</a> Rumbula <a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=13/56.88420/24.23970\">https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=13/56.88420/24.23970</a> .</p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=13/56.94240/24.23524\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/6216f4773cbede236f0589ddcc1cf59e83a3b7bb/68747470733a2f2f7777772e6f70656e7374726565746d61702e6f72672f6173736574732f6f736d5f6c6f676f5f3235362d656430323866393034363832323461323732393631633338306563656530636662373362383034386233346634623462323034623766306431303937383735642e706e67&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=13/56.94240/24.23524\" title=\"OpenStreetMap\">OpenStreetMap</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">OpenStreetMap is a map of the world, created by people like you and free to use under an open license.</div></div></div><div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=14/56.98753/24.30335\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/6216f4773cbede236f0589ddcc1cf59e83a3b7bb/68747470733a2f2f7777772e6f70656e7374726565746d61702e6f72672f6173736574732f6f736d5f6c6f676f5f3235362d6564303238663930343638323234613237323936316333383065636565306366623733623830343862333466346234623230346237663064313039373837